  "body": "**üíª Environment**\r\n\r\nUUPSUpgradeable.sol uses the same implementation slot as ERC1967 which goes agains ERC1822 specification\r\n\r\n\r\n\"However, rather than forcing use of a variable, the address of the Logic Contract is stored at the defined storage position keccak256(\"PROXIABLE\"). This eliminates the possibility of collision between variables in the Proxy and Logic Contracts, thus providing ‚Äúuniversal‚Äù compatibility with any Logic Contract.\"",
